{"about_the_game":"The Xbox Live Indie Game classic returns! One part crafting game and one part 2D platformer, <i>Craftimals</i> lets you build your own way to the top! Play single-player or local co-op and help the animals reach the sun. Checkpoints along the way give you new powers and hats. Find out what happens when you touch the sun, or simply have fun building!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Intuitive building mechanics<br></li><li> Relaxing, combat-free gameplay<br></li><li> A large, open canvas to &quot;paint&quot; on<br></li><li> 2-player splitscreen co-op</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What's New</h2><br>This is mostly a direct port of the game that was originally released in 2012. The only adjustments that have been made are new keyboard/mouse controls, new music by Audionautix, and Steam-specific goodies (achievements, leaderboards, etc.). If you want to suggest further improvements, then please see our other game, <i>Doggo Dig Down</i>, which is the &quot;spiritual successor&quot; to <i>Craftimals</i>.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Checkpoint #1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3172430/d69b754d2912c30dc8f677414cf1e635805f1f4d.jpg"},{"name":"Checkpoint #2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3172430/d69b754d2912c30dc8f677414cf1e635805f1f4d.jpg"},{"name":"Checkpoint #3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3172430/d69b754d2912c30dc8f677414cf1e635805f1f4d.jpg"},{"name":"Checkpoint #4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3172430/d69b754d2912c30dc8f677414cf1e635805f1f4d.jpg"},{"name":"Checkpoint #5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3172430/d69b754d2912c30dc8f677414cf1e635805f1f4d.jpg"},{"name":"Checkpoint #6","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3172430/d69b754d2912c30dc